## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited selection of sources and may not encompass all perspectives on successful management. Additionally, the reliance on online articles and community discussions may introduce bias, as these sources may not always reflect the latest academic research or industry trends. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of what makes a successful manager.